snippet.title: Five Nights At Freddy's Security Breach: Blast to the Past! Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
https://gamebanana.com/wips/78055

Blast to the Past! is a mod for Security Breach that restores a lot of its cut-content and adds some new stuff as well! This mod is a work in progress, so see you later Superstar!

Video edited by ShiftyNifty
